column5: Thank you for your words. Made my morning happy which I haven't experienced for a long time.

Same here I created a POS app for restaurant. But hygiene is a primary factor and customers may feel bad when they see waiters using smartphones in front of them. This was said by one of the restaurants I approach with my app. 
Were you able to build a strong customer base for your POS platform?
Hi you are right. I do have 12 customers using the app. I am trying to get more users to using it..
Thanks for the help. My app is an free order management app for restaurants.
I received the Android 10 update for my Galaxy Note 9 in India.
Happy Birthday, thank you for informing us. We are here for you
